ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 222, Alberta
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 222 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the Minister to provide financial assistance to the province of ALBERTA, with respect to the interface fires that occurred from May 18 to June 26, 2019.
